  <brief_title>Intense Pulsed Light Therapy for Hidrosadenitis Suppurativa</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Intense Pulsed Light Assisted Hair Removal Therapy on Mild and Moderate Cases of Hidrosadenitis Suppurativa</official_title>
