  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      6 monthly treatments with IPL laser in patients with Hidradenitis Suppurativa. The effect in
      measured on several severity scores.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patient suffering from bilateral HS in the axilla or groin area are threated with IPL laser
      monthly for 6 months.

      Patients are randomized to treatment in either left or right side, the other side works as
      control.

      No sham treatment, but observers are blinded.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
